document_data.name: Immar Fardelver
document_data.mainbody: '''Immar Fardelver''' was an artisan of [[Delzoun]] in the 4th century before [[Dalereckoning]].
document_data.History: In the [[-335 DR|Year of Seven Spirits, −335 DR]], Immar Fardelver was commissioned by [[Maerin]] of [[Illusk]], alongside many other dwarven artisans from Delzoun, for the building of [[Gauntlgrym]]. The work was completed in the [[-321 DR|Year of Hollow Hills, −321 DR]].
